subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Having beaten Maria Sharapova just once in four tries going into the match, the German Angelique Kerber survived a grueling battle to upset the five-time Grand Slam champion and advance to Wimbledon’s women’s quarterfinals.
